openastro-phd2 (2.0.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Rename Debian source/binary package phd2-alpaca -> openastro-phd2 to match
    the macOS bundle identifier (net.openastro.phd2) and Windows installer
    branding. Existing installs of phd2-alpaca must be `apt remove`d before
    installing this package; Conflicts/Replaces metadata covers the dpkg path.
  * System user, group, install paths, and systemd unit all renamed accordingly
    (/var/lib/phd2-alpaca -> /var/lib/openastro-phd2, etc.).
  * See CHANGELOG.md for the full 2.0.0 release notes.

 -- Joey Troy <joey.troy@gmail.com>  Fri, 15 May 2026 12:00:00 -0600

phd2-alpaca (1.3.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Re-add INDI camera, mount, and rotator support on all platforms.
  * Add INDI server auto-discovery (subnet probe on port 7624).
  * Fix INDI camera first-exposure disconnect by waiting for CCD_INFO.
  * Auto-populate pixel size in profile wizard for INDI cameras.
  * Bump pinned vcpkg to 2024.11.16 and parallelize Windows build.
  * Add OpenAstro favicon for embedded web portal.
  * See CHANGELOG.md for detailed release notes.

 -- Joey Troy <joey.troy@gmail.com>  Tue, 12 May 2026 20:00:00 -0600

