phd2-alpaca (1.0.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial OpenAstro PHD2 Alpaca release.
  * Renamed package from phd2 to phd2-alpaca.
  * Linux .deb build support and Alpaca Linux packaging/build updates.
  * Headless systemd service running as dedicated phd2-alpaca system user.

